{"tid":1591721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]唔好再講下一次，十月一日就係背水一戰就係總決戰","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T00:07:27.000Z","uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"762630f8839097a0c003d3e8ee248a2e49cbdad3","tid":1591721,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"無ga la<br />\n十月一日就係決戰，無下一次，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係唔會再有</span></span><br />\n過左十月一之後可能香港人都唔撚再存在<br />\n可能解放軍入城屠城未定<br />\n可能緊急法拉晒成個連登既人未定<br />\n可能直接暗殺晒抗爭者都未定<br />\n可能乜事都無都未定<br />\n即然未來唔知係點，就要活在當下<br />\n十月一係唯一一次機會<br />\n係全世界望住你既決心，可以撤撤底底咁落鳩支那面<br />\n唔會再有下一次，亦無下一個機會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一<br />\nFight like there's no tomorrow<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a5ba8a562bed761273e9b2e418751fd71410c6cb","tid":1591721,"uid":28010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f743f5dce2b5b49ae48086f2aad3cf97606d984a","tid":1591721,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"7a561af7406447e6ac2da8e4d781e247a6ad4a63","tid":1591721,"uid":259329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:27:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79d7ab5fbea6117e2c4d7d6040ded0dce5a468e4","tid":1591721,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><s